name: title
Kononenko 5mm beam JTDKE 12 wks: Kinematic of 12-week-old JTDKE mice walking on a 5 mm wide beam

name: description
Kononenko 5mm beam JTDKE 12 wks: Original SIMI videos, DeepLabCut-tracked videos and csv files of body kinematics of 12-week-old VGAT-Cre;Atg5flox/flox;GLUT2flox/flox mice walking on a wide 5 mm beam. Mixed group of control and mutant mice. Individual trials for each mouse are recorded from 8 cameras and metadata for synchronization is stored as *.smp files.
